text:
There He is, standing in the Seven Golden Candlesticks. Now:
Unto the … church of Ephesus write; These things write, these things which saith he that holdeth the seven stars in his right hand, who walketh in the midst of the seven golden candlesticks;
I know thy works … (Remember, you're not forgotten.) I know thy works, and thy labor, and thy patience, and … thou canst not bear them which are evil…
